hadiths[7]{hadithnumber,text}:
1,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke tamam aamaal ka daro-madar niyat par hai aur har amal ka nateeja har insan ko uski niyat ke mutabiq hi milega. to jiski hijrat ( tarke-watan ( dolate-duniya hasil karne ke liye ho ya kisi aurat se shadi ki gharaz ho. to uski hijrat un hi chizon ke liye hogi jinke hasil karne ki niyat se usne hijrat ki hai.
2,Haris-bin-Hisham naam ke aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya tha ke ya Rasulullah ! aap par wahi kaisey nazil hoti hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wahi nazil hotey waqt kabhi mujh ko ghanti ki si awaz mehsus hoti hai aur wahi ki ye kaifiyat mujh par bahut sakht guzarti hai. jab ye kaifiyat khatm hoti hai to mere dil w dimagh par us ( Farishtey (ke zariey nazil shuda wahi mehfooz ho jati hai aur kisi waqt aisa hota hai ke farishta insan ki shakl mein mere paas aata hai aur mujh se kalam karta hai. isliye main uska kaha hua yad rakh leta hun. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke maine sakht kadake ki sardi main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil hui aur jab iska silsila ruka to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki peshani pasiney se sharabor thi.
3,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi ka shuruati daur achchhey, sachey aur pakeeza khuwabon se shuru hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khuwab mein jo kuchh dekhtey wo subah ki roshni ki tarah sahi aur sachcha Sabit hota. phir qudrat ki taraf se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tanhai pasand ho gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghare-hira main tanhai ikhtiyar farmai aur kai-kai din aur raat wahan musalsal ibadat aur yade-Ilahi w zikr w fikr mein mashghool rehtey. jab tak ghar aaney ko dil na chahta khane-pine ka saman sath liye huey wahan rehtey. khane-pine ka saman khatm honey par hi ahliya mohtarma Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas tashrif latey aur kuchh khane-pine ka saman sath lekar phir wahan ja kar tanhai mein chale jatey, yahi tariqa jari raha yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par haq khul gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghare-hira hi mein thahre huey they ke achcha Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huey aur kehney lagey ke aey Muhammad! padho, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey hain ke maine kaha ke main padhna nahi janta, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey hain ke Farishtey ne mujhey pakad kar itney zor se bheencha ke meri taqat jawab de gaee, phir mujhey chhod kar kaha ke padho, maine phir wahi jawab diya ke main padha hua nahi hun. us Farishtey ne mujh ko bahut hi zor se bheencha ke mujh ko sakht takleef mehsus hui, phir usne kaha ke padh! maine kaha ke main padha hua nahi hun. Farishtey ne teesri baar mujh ko pakda aur teesri martaba phir mujh ko bheencha phir mujhey chhod diya aur kehney laga ke padho apne rab ke naam ki madad se jisne paida kya aur insan ko khoon ki phutkii se banaya, padho aur aap ka rab bahut hi meharbaniyan karne wala hai. to yahi aayatein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) se sun kar is haal mein ghare-hira se wapas huey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka dil us anokhe waqiey se kanp raha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Khadija ke yahan tashrif laey aur farmaya ke mujhey kambal odha do, mujhey kambal udha do. logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kambal udha diya. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka dar jata raha. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni bevi mohtarma Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ko tafseel ke sath ye waqia sunaya aur farmaney lagey ke mujh ko ab apni jaan ka khof ho gaya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya mohtarma Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dharas bandhai aur kaha ke aap ka khayal sahi nahi hai. Allah ki qasam! aapko Allah kabhi ruswa nahi karega, aap to behtreen akhlaq ke Malik hain, aap to kunba parwar hain, be-kason ka bojh apne sar par rakh letey hain, muflison ke liye aap kamatey hain, mehman nawazi mein aap be-misal hain aur mushkil waqt mein aap haq baat ka sath detey hain. aisi khoobiyon wala insan yun be-waqat, zillat w ruswai ki maut nahi pa sakta. phir mazeed tasalli ke liye Khadija (Raziallahu anha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Warqa-bin-Naufal ke paas le gain, jo unke chacha-zad bhai they aur zamana-e-jahiliyat mein nasrani mazhab ikhtiyar kar chukey they aur Ibranii zaban ke kaatib they, chunanche Injeel ko bhi hasbe-manshaey-khudawandi Ibranii zaban mein likha kartey they. (injeel suryani zaban mein nazil hui thi phir iska tarjama Ibranii zaban mein hua. Warqa-usii ko likhtey they) wo bahut boodhe ho gaey they yahan tak ke unki aankh ki roshni bhi ja chuki thi. Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ne unke samney Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke halaat bayan kiye aur kaha ke aey chacha-zad bhai! apne bhatijey (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ki zabani zara unki kaifiyat sun lijiye. wo boley ke bhatijey aap ne jo kuchh dekha hai, uski tafseel sunao. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shuru se aakhir tak pura waqia sunaya, jisey sun kar Warqa be-ikhtiyaar ho kar bol uthey ke ye to wahi namus (muazzaz raazdaan farishta) hai jisey Allah ne Musa (Alaihissalam) par wahi dekar bheja tha. kaash, mein aap ke us ahade-nubuwat ke shuru honey par jawan-umr hota. kaash, main us waqt tak zinda rehta jabke aap ki qaum aapko us Shahar se nikal degi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sun kar tajjub se puchha ke kya wo log mujh ko nikal dengey? (halanke main to unmein sadiq w ameen w maqbool hun) Warqa bola haan ye sab kuchh sach hai. magar jo shakhs bhi aap ki tarah haq baat lekar aaya log iske dushman hi ho gaey hain. agar mujhey aap ki nabwooat ka wo zamana mil jaey to main aap ki poori-poori madad karunga. magar Warqa kuchh dinon ke baad intiqal kar gaey. phir kuchh arse tak wahi ki aamad ruki rahi."
4,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahi ke ruk janey ke zamaney ke halaat bayan farmatey huey kaha ke aik roz main chala ja raha tha ke achcha maine aasman ki taraf aik awaz suni aur maine apna sar aasman ki taraf uthaya. kya dekhta hun ke wahi farishta jo mere paas ghare-hira mein aaya tha wo aasman w zameen ke beech mein aik kursi par betha hua hai. main us se dar gaya aur ghar aaney par maine phir kambal odhney ki khahish zahir ki. us waqt Allah paak ki taraf se ye aayatein nazil huin. aey lihaf odh kar letney waley ! uth khada ho aur logon ko azabe-Ilahi se dara aur apne rab ki badaai bayan kar aur apne kapdon ko paak saaf rakh aur gandagi se door reh. iske baad wahi tezi ke sath pai-dar-pai aaney lagi is hadis ko Yahya-bin-Bukair ke ilawa Lais-bin-Sad se Abdullah-bin Yusuf aur Abu-Saleh ne bhi riwayat kya hai. aur Aqeel ke ilawa Zohri se Hilaal-bin-Rawaad ne bhi riwayat kya hai. Yunus aur Mamar ne apni riwayat mein lafz ( فواده ( ki jagah ( بوادره ( naql kya hai.
5,"unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kalame-Ilahi (لا تحرك به لسانك لتعجل به‏) (75:16) ki tafseer ke silsile mein suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nuzool-e-Quran ke waqt bahut sakhti mehsus farmaya kartey they aur uski ( alamaton ( mein se aik ye thi ke yad karne ke liye aap apne honton ko hilatey they. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main apne hont hilata hun jis tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hilatey they. Saeed kehtey hain main bhi apne hont hilata hun jis tarah Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko maine hilatey dekha. phir unhon-ne apne hont hilaey. (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha) phir ye aayat utri ke aey Muhammad! Quran ko jaldi-jaldi yad karne ke liye apni zaban na hilao. iska jama kar dena aur padha dena hamara zimma hai. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain yani Quran Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke dil mein jama dena aur padha dena hamarey zimme hai. phir jab ham padh chukein to us padhey huey ki ittaba (pairvi) karo. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ( iska matlab ye hai) ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko khamoshi ke sath suntey raho. iske baad matlab samjha dena hamarey zimme hai. phir yaqinan ye hamari zimme-dari hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko padho (yani usko mehfooz kar sako ( chunanche iske baad jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ( wahi lekar ( aatey to aap ( tawajjoh se) suntey . jab wo chaley jatey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us ( wahi ( ko isi tarah padhtey jis tarah Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne usey padha tha."
6,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sab logon se zyada karam-farma aur data they aur Ramazan mein (doosrey waqton ke muqable mein jab) Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se miltey bahut hi zyada sakhawat w karam farmatey. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Ramazan ki har raat mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mulaqat kartey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Quran ka daura kartey, gharaz Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ko bhalai pahunchaney mein barish laney wali hawa se bhi zyada sakhawat w karam farmaya kartey they."
7,"Hiraql ( Rome ke badshah ( ne unke paas Quraish ke qafley mein aik aadmi bulaney ko bheja aur us waqt ye log tijarat ke liye mulk Sham (Syria) gaey huey they aur ye wo zamana tha jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Quraish aur Abu-Sufiyan se aik waqti ahad kya hua tha. jab Abu-Sufiyan aur doosrey log Hiraql ke paas Iliyaa pahunchey jahan Hiraql ne darbar talab kya tha. uske gird Rome (mojooda Itly) ke badey-badey log (ulama, wazeer aur ameer ( baithey huey they. Hiraql ne unko aur apne tarjuman ko bulwaya . phir unse puchha ke tum mein se kon shakhs risalat ke dawedar ka zyada qaribi azeez hai? Abu-Sufiyan kehtey hain ke main bol utha ke main uska sabse zyada qaribi rishtedar hun. (ye sun kar) Hiraql ne hukm diya ke usko ( Abu-Sufiyan ko) mere qareeb la kar bithao aur uske sathiyon ko uski peeth ke peechhey bitha do. phir apne tarjuman se kaha ke un logon se keh do ke main Abu-Sufiyan se us shakhs ke (yani Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke) halaat poochhta hun. agar ye mujh se kisi baat mein jhoot bol de to tum iska jhoot zahir kar dena. ( Abu-Sufiyan ka kehna hai ke) Allah ki qism ! agar mujhey ye ghairat na aati ke ye log mujh ko jhutlaenge to main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nisbat zaroor jhoot se kaam leta . khair pehli baat jo Hiraql ne mujh se poochhi wo ye ke us shakhs ka khandan tum logon mein kaisa hai? maine kaha wo to badey oonchey khandan waley aur aali nasb hain. kehney laga is se pahley bhi kisi ne tum logon mein aisi baat kahi thi? maine kaha nahi. kehney laga, achchha iske badon mein koi badshah hua hai? maine kaha nahi. phir us ne kaha, badey logon ne uski pairwi ikhtiyar ki hai ya kamzoron ne ? maine kaha nahi kamzoron ne. phir kehney laga, iske perokar roz badhtey jatey hain ya koi sathi phir bhi jata hai? maine kaha nahi. kehney laga ke kya apne us daawe (nubuwat) se pahley kabhi ( kisi bhi mauqe par) us ne jhoot bola hai? maine kaha nahi. aur ab hamari us se (Suleh ki) aik muqarrara muddat tay hui hai. malum nahi wo usmein kya karne wala hai. ( Abu-Sufiyan kehtey hain) main is baat ke siwa aur koi (jhoot) us baat-cheet mein shamil na kar saka. Hiraql ne kaha kya tumhari us se kabhi ladai bhi hoti hai? ham ne kaha ke haan. bola phir tumhari aur uski jang ka kya haal hota hai? maine kaha, ladai dol ki tarah hai, kabhi wo ham se (maidane-jang) jeet letey hain aur kabhi ham unse jeet letey hain. Hiraql ne poochha. wo tumhen kis baat ka hukm deta hai? maine kaha wo kehta hai ke sirf aik Allah hi ki ibadat karo, uska kisi ko Sharik na banao aur apne bap-dada ki (shirk ki) baatein chhod do aur hamein Namaz padhney, sach bolney, parhezgari aur sila rehmii ka hukm deta hai. (ye sab sun kar) phir Hiraql ne apne tarjuman se kaha ke Abu-Sufiyan se keh de ke maine tum se iska nasb puchha to tum ne kaha ke wo ham mein aalii-nasb hai aur paighambar apni qaum mein aali nasb hi bhejey jaya kartey hain. maine tum se puchha ke) dawa-e-nabwooat ki) ye baat tumharey andar us se pahley kisi aur ne bhi kahi thi, to tum ne jawab diya ke nahi, tab maine (apne dil mein) kaha ke agar ye baat us se pahley kisi ne kahi hoti to main samajhta ke us shakhs ne bhi usi baat ki pairvi ki hai jo pahley kahi ja chuki hai. maine tum se puchha ke iske badon mein koi badshah bhi guzra hai, tum ne kaha ke nahi. to maine (dil mein) kaha ke unke buzurgon mein se koi badshah hua hoga to keh doonga ke wo shakhs (is bahaney) apne bap-dada ki badhshahat aur unka mulk ( dobara ( hasil karna chahta hai. aur maine tum se puchha ke is baat ke kehney (yani paighambari ka dawa karne) se pahley tum ne kabhi usko jhoot bolne ka ilzam lagaya hai? tum ne kaha ke nahi. to maine samajh liya ke jo shakhs aadmiyon ke sath jhoot se bachey wo Allah ke barey mein kaisey jhooti baat keh sakta hai. aur maine tum se puchha ke badey log iske pairo hotey hain ya kamzor aadmi. tum ne kaha kamzoron ne uski ittaba (pairvi) ki hai, to ( dar-asl ( yahi log paighambaron ke perokar hotey hain. aur maine tum se puchha ke uske sathi badh rahe hain ya kam ho rahe hain. tum ne kaha ke wo badh rahe hain aur eman ki kaifiyat yahi hoti hai. yahan tak ke wo kaamil ho jata hai aur maine tum se puchha ke aaya koi shakhs iske Deen se naakhush ho kar murtad bhi ho jata hai tum ne kaha nahi, to eman ki khaasiyat bhi yahi hai jinke dilon mein uski musarrat rach-bas jaey wo us se lota nahi kartey aur maine tum se puchha ke aaya wo kabhi ahad shikanii kartey hain. tum ne kaha nahi, paighambaron ka yahi haal hota hai, wo ahad ki khilaf warzi nahi kartey aur maine tum se kaha ke wo tum se kis cheez ke liye kehtey hain. tum ne kaha ke wo hamein hukm detey hain ke Allah ki ibadat karo, iske sath kisi ko Sharik na thehrao aur tumhen buton ki parastish se roktey hain. sach bolney aur parhezgari ka hukm detey hain. lihaza agar ye baatein jo tum keh rahe ho sach hain to bahut jald wo us jagah ka Malik ho jaeyga ke jahan mere ye donon paon hain. mujhey malum tha ke wo ( paighambar ( aaney wala hai. magar mujhey ye malum nahi tha ke wo tumharey andar hoga. agar main janta ke us tak pahunch sakunga to usse milney ke liye har takleef gawara karta. agar main uske paas hota to uske paon dhota. Hiraql ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka wo khat mangaya jo aap ne Dahiya Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) ke zariey hakime-Basra ke paas bheja tha aur usne wo Hiraql ke paas bhej diya tha. phir usko padha to usmein ( likha tha) : Allah ke naam ke sath jo bahut hi zyada meharban aur raham wala hai. Allah ke bandey aur uske paighambar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se ye khat hai Rome ke badshah ke liye. us shakhs par salam ho jo hidayat ki pairwi karey iske baad main aap ke samney dawate-Islam pesh karta hun. agar aap Islam ley aaengey to (deen w duniya mein) salamati naseeb hogi. Allah aapko dohra sawab dega aur agar aap (meri dawat se) inkar karengey to aap ki riaya ka gunah bhi aap hi par hoga aur aey ahle-kitab! aik aisi baat par aa jao jo hamarey aur tumharey darmyan yaksan hai. wo ye ke ham Allah ke siwa kisi ki ibadat na karein aur kisi ko uska Sharik na thehraein aur na ham mein se koi kisi ko Allah ke siwa apna rab banaey. phir agar wo ahle-kitab (is baat se) munh pher lein to ( musalmanon!) tum unse keh do ke (tum maano ya na maano ( ham to aik Allah ke itaat guzaar hain. Abu-Sufiyan kehtey hain : jab Hiraql ne jo kuchh kehna tha keh diya aur khat padh kar farigh hua to uske ird-gird bahut shor w ghogha hua, bahut si aawazein uthin aur hamein bahar nikal diya gaya. tab maine apne sathiyon se kaha ke abu-Kabsha ki betey (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ka mamla to bahut badh gaya (dekho to) us se bani-asfar (Rome (mojooda Itly)) ka badshah bhi darta hai. mujhey us waqt se is baat ka yaqin ho gaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) an-qareeb ghalib ho kar rahengey. yahan tak ke Allah ne mujhey musalman kar diya. ( rawi ka bayan hai ke) ibne-Naatoor iiliyaa ka Hakim Hiraql ka masaahib aur Sham (Syria) ke nasara ka laat paadrii bayan karta tha ke Hiraql jab iiliyaa aaya, aik din subah ko pareshan utha to iske darbaariyon ne malum kya ke aaj ham aap ki haalat badli hui patey hain. (kya wjah hai? ( ibne-Naatoor ka bayan hai ke Hiraql Nujoomi (Astrologer) tha, ilme-Nujoom (Astrology) mein wo poori maharat rakhta tha. usne apne sathi ko bataya ke maine aaj raat sitaron par nazar dali to dekha ke khatna karne walon ka badshah hamarey mulk par ghalib aa gaya hai. ( bhala (us zamaney mein kon log khatna kartey hain? unhon-ne kaha ke yahood ke siwa koi khatna nahi karta. so unki wjah se pareshan na hun. saltanat ke tamam shehron mein ye hukm likh bhejiye ke wahan jitney Yahudi hon sab qatl kar diye jaaein. wo log unhi baton mein mashghool they ke Hiraql ke paas aik aadmi laya gaya. jisey shahe-ghassan ne bheja tha. usne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke halaat bayan kiye. jab Hiraql ne (sarey halaat) sun liye to kaha ke ja kar dekho wo khatna kiye huey hai ya nahi? unhon-ne usey dekha to batlaya ke wo khatna kya hua hai. Hiraql ne jab us shakhs se Arab ke barey mein puchha to usne batlaya ke wo khatna kartey hain. tab Hiraql ne kaha ke ye hi ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) is ummat ke badshah hain jo paida ho chukey hain. phir us ne apne aik dost ko roomiya khat likha aur wo bhi ilme-Nujoom (Astrology) mein Hiraql ki tarah maahir tha. phir wahan se Hiraql teiswin chala gaya. abhi teiswin se nikla nahi tha ke iske dost ka khat (iske jawab mein) aa gaya. uski raey bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zuhoor ke barey mein Hiraql ke muwafiq thi ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( waqei ( paighambar hain. iske baad Hiraql ne Rome (mojooda Itly) ke badey aadmiyon ko apne teiswin ke mahal mein talab kya aur uske hukm se mahal ke darwazey band kar liye gaey. phir wo (apne khas mahal se) bahar aaya aur kaha ''aey Rome waalo! kya hidayat aur kamiyabi mein kuchh hissey tumharey liye bhi hai? agar tum apni saltanat ki baqaa chahtey ho to phir us Nabi ki bait kar lo aur musalman ho jao '' (ye sunnaa tha ke) phir wo log wahshii gadhon ki tarah darwazon ki taraf daudey ( magar ( unhein band paya. aakhir jab Hiraql ne (is baat se) unki ye nafrat dekhi aur unke eman laney se maayoos ho gaya to kehney laga ke un logon ko mere paas laao. (jab wo dobara aaey ( to usne kaha maine jo baat kahi thi us se tumhari deeni pukhtagi ki aazmaish maqsud thi so wo maine dekh li. tab (ye baat sun kar) wo sab ke sab uske samney sajdey mein gir padey aur us se khush ho gaey. bil-aakhir Hiraql ki aakhiri haalat ye hi rahi. abu-Adbullah kehtey hain ke us hadis ko Saleh bin kaisaan , Yunus aur Mamar ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya hai."
